if it's an infinite barrier?

00:08:20.299 --> 00:08:22.090
PROFESSOR: If there's
two wells and there's

00:08:22.090 --> 00:08:24.370
an infinite barrier
between them,

00:08:24.370 --> 00:08:26.600
