00:08:59.170 --> 00:09:01.140
But it's a little more delicate.

00:09:01.140 --> 00:09:02.840
But certainly two
potentials that

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:05.030
are separated by
an infinite barrier

00:09:05.030 --> 00:09:10.440
is not part of what we
really want to consider.

